	*) Calling constructors

	*) Bean references

	*) Array construction

	*) Inline lists

	*) Inline maps

	*) Ternary operator

	*) Variables

	*) User defined functions

	*) Collection projection

	*) Collection selection

	*) Templated expressions
	


